data.description: Great home located in the Heart of Fort Oglethorpe, convenient to shopping, medical offices, parks and all the  conveniences of living in the city.  The home offers lots of space to enjoy with 3 bedrooms and 4 baths.  Hardwoods and vinyl throughout the home. The front room was added as a bedroom, but could also be used as additional living space. Nice size kitchen with dining area, the washer and dryer was moved from the back laundry room into the kitchen area for convenience but could be moved back into the laundry area.  The nice screened in porch on the front of the home is a great place to sit and enjoy and there is also a nice sunroom on the back of the home for your backyard enjoyment along with a  level fenced in backyard. This home is ready for you to Call Home, make your showing today..  The listing agent is related to the seller.  Seller is the uncle of listing agent's Spouse.
